    {
      "Text": "The Go Programming Language.\n\nSecurity Fix(es):\n\nnet/http in Go before 1.16.12 and 1.17.x before 1.17.5 allows uncontrolled memory consumption in the header canonicalization cache via HTTP/2 requests.(CVE-2021-44716)",
      "Title": "Description",
      "Type": "General"
    },
    {
